OL,3,CANDYSMANCLUB to host 12-hour
OL,4,Cconversation for men's mental health
OL,6,FA national movement that supports over
OL,7,F6,000 men every week is hosting a 12-
OL,8,Fhour conversation to raise awareness
OL,9,Fabout men's mental health.
OL,11,FANDYSMANCLUB was set up in 2016 when
OL,12,FAndrew Roberts took his own life at
OL,13,Fthe age of 23.
OL,15,FAndy's family had no idea he was
OL,16,Fstruggling with his mental health, and
OL,17,Fas a result looked deeper into male
OL,18,Fsuicide and men's mental health.
OL,20,FThey soon discovered that male suicide
OL,21,Fis the biggest killer of men under 54.
