OL,3,CANDYSMANCLUB to host 12-hour
OL,4,Cconversation for men's mental health
OL,6,FElaine Roberts, Andy's mum, and Luke
OL,7,FAmbler, his brother-in-law, came up
OL,8,Fwith the idea of ANDYSMANCLUB - a
OL,9,Fgroup where men can speak openly about
OL,10,Ftheir mental health.
OL,12,FWhat started in Halifax with a group
OL,13,Fof nine men, has now spread from
OL,14,FAberdeen to Plymouth.
OL,16,FOn Wednesday 27 August, ANDYSMANCLUB
OL,17,Fis holding a 12-hour conversation in
OL,18,FLondon.
