OL,3,CANDYSMANCLUB to host 12-hour
OL,4,Cconversation for men's mental health
OL,6,FThere will be a range of people from
OL,7,Finfluencers to celebrities, targeting
OL,8,Fdifferent age groups, all with the aim
OL,9,Fof breaking the stigma and getting
OL,10,Fmore men to speak up.
OL,12,FLuke Ambler said: "12 men die every
OL,13,Fsingle day in this country - that's
OL,14,Fone man every two hours. So for every
OL,15,Fhour we're going (with the event),
OL,16,Ftragically someone statistically will
OL,17,Fdie by suicide.
