OL,3,CANDYSMANCLUB to host 12-hour
OL,4,Cconversation for men's mental health
OL,6,F"What we've got to do is continue to
OL,7,Fkeep having those conversations, keep
OL,8,Fbreaking the stigmas that those
OL,9,Fconversations are okay to have, and
OL,10,Fkeep delivering that bit of light in
OL,11,Fpeople's dark time.
OL,13,F"So I think the longest conversation
OL,14,Frepresents a host of things to
OL,15,Fdifferent people.
OL,17,F"What we're ultimately trying to do is
OL,18,Fnot just start a conversation, but to
OL,19,Fgive people something to smile about."
