OL,3,CANDYSMANCLUB to host 12-hour
OL,4,Cconversation for men's mental health
OL,6,FWhen asked about how ANDYSMANCLUB has
OL,7,Fgrown, Luke said: "It's phenomenal. I
OL,8,Fpinch myself sometimes, but also I
OL,9,Fstay very grounded in the fact that
OL,10,Fwe've still got a lot of work to do.
OL,12,F"We've got to continue now to keep
OL,13,Fbanging that drum, keep letting people
OL,14,Fknow it's okay to talk, but also keep
OL,15,Fproviding that weekly safe space for
OL,16,Fthem to do so.
OL,18,F"On one hand it's really amazing, on
OL,19,Fthe other hand it's very tragic that
OL,20,Fwe're needed."
